description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Gaston purrs with a rating of 81, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 81, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 1 for East, 3 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60811-11360-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [81 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
